Guys, are you sure we shouldn't tell anybody

524
00:26:21,340 --> 00:26:25,900
that there is a sentient paper hallmaster monitor

525
00:26:25,900 --> 00:26:27,180
being in the basement?

526
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:29,100
I don't want to tell Tally.

527
00:26:29,100 --> 00:26:30,860
She's just going to go down there.

528
00:26:31,500 --> 00:26:31,980
Yeah.

529
00:26:31,980 --> 00:26:33,660
Yeah, no, we don't want the kids to know.

530
00:26:33,660 --> 00:26:34,540
I mean, that was the one hard question I had, so.

531
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:35,340
Yeah, but like.

532
00:26:37,820 --> 00:26:38,380
Okay.

533
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:38,780
Is it responsible?

534
00:26:38,780 --> 00:26:39,660
What's the benefit?

535
00:26:40,620 --> 00:26:42,140
What's the benefit of letting someone know?

536
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:44,220
In case he gets out.

537
00:26:45,980 --> 00:26:48,220
Never got out before, and he's been there

538
00:26:48,220 --> 00:26:49,980
for like 250 years.

539
00:26:51,020 --> 00:26:53,180
All right, so what you're saying is

540
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:57,180
you guys will be held responsible if anything happens.

541
00:26:57,180 --> 00:27:00,620
Well, I don't love the way that's framed.

542
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:01,900
I mean, that's kind of how it's been.

543
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:05,259
I mean, you know, Cav literally went on trial for something.

544
00:27:05,259 --> 00:27:05,580
True.

545
00:27:05,580 --> 00:27:06,700
So we're kind of.

546
00:27:06,700 --> 00:27:07,500
You know what?

547
00:27:07,500 --> 00:27:10,380
We kind of are responsible, I guess, actually.

548
00:27:10,380 --> 00:27:11,099
Thanks, Buzzard.

549
00:27:11,099 --> 00:27:11,740
You're right.

550
00:27:11,740 --> 00:27:12,380
Yeah.

551
00:27:12,380 --> 00:27:14,380
It sounded bad, but it's just accurate.

552
00:27:14,380 --> 00:27:17,579
Yeah, we're responsible for everything that happens to us.

553
00:27:17,579 --> 00:27:19,339
So we're kind of responsible.

554
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:21,680
Okay.

555
00:27:22,460 --> 00:27:22,960
Okay.

556
00:27:23,420 --> 00:27:25,180
Do you feel okay, Alydin?

557
00:27:25,180 --> 00:27:26,460
Yeah, I guess so.

558
00:27:26,460 --> 00:27:28,140
See, if we told somebody and they went down there

559
00:27:28,140 --> 00:27:30,380
and got hurt, we'd also be responsible for that.

560
00:27:32,059 --> 00:27:33,819
Damned if you do, damned if you don't.

561
00:27:33,819 --> 00:27:34,779
That's right.

562
00:27:34,779 --> 00:27:35,980
Okay, fair.

563
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:39,339
Are we bringing Alistair to Lingersville?

564
00:27:40,059 --> 00:27:41,099
Oh, um.

565
00:27:41,099 --> 00:27:42,860
Yeah, we need a tester.

